{"word":"H7437 - רָמַת לֶחִי - Râmath Lechîy - raw'-math lekh'-ee - Ramath-lehi","slug":"H7437","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">רָמַת לֶחִי</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Râmath Lechîy"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>raw'-math lekh'-ee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Ramath-lehi"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>רמת לחי</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>râmath lechı̂y</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>raw'-math lekh'-ee</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Ramath-lehi = \"height of a jawbone\" <ol><li>a place by the rock Elam in northern Judah near the border of the Philistines; named by Samson after his slaughter of the 1000 Philistines with the jawbone of an ass</li></ol> <p />Origin: from <a href=\"#/H7413\">H7413</a> and <a href=\"#/H3895\">H3895</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Location "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4791\">H4791</a>, <a href=\"#/H7216\">H7216</a>, <a href=\"#/H7311\">H7311</a>, <a href=\"#/H7312\">H7312</a>, <a href=\"#/H7315\">H7315</a>, <a href=\"#/H7316\">H7316</a>, <a href=\"#/H7317\">H7317</a>, <a href=\"#/H7318\">H7318</a>, <a href=\"#/H7319\">H7319</a>, <a href=\"#/H7320\">H7320</a>, <a href=\"#/H7410\">H7410</a>, <a href=\"#/H7413\">H7413</a>, <a href=\"#/H7414\">H7414</a>, <a href=\"#/H7418\">H7418</a>, <a href=\"#/H7419\">H7419</a>, <a href=\"#/H7427\">H7427</a>, <a href=\"#/H7432\">H7432</a>, <a href=\"#/H7433\">H7433</a>, <a href=\"#/H7434\">H7434</a>, <a href=\"#/H7435\">H7435</a>, <a href=\"#/H8641\">H8641</a>, <a href=\"#/H8642\">H8642</a>"}]}